data.description: Welcome to your modern oasis in the heart of Tatum, TX! This stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home, built in 2021, offers contemporary living at its finest.  As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an open-concept living space flooded with natural light, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet family evenings. The spacious living area seamlessly flows into the gourmet kitchen, boasting sleek stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar.  The master suite is a true retreat, featuring a generous walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom complete with dual vanitiy and a walk-in shower. Two additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family members or guests, each offering ample closet space and easy access to the second full bathroom. Conveniently located in the charming town of Tatum, this home offers easy access to local schools, parks, shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Whether you're commuting to nearby cities or exploring the natural beauty of East Texas, this prime location has it all.  Don't miss your opportunity to make this beautiful home yours! Schedule your showing today and start living the lifestyle you deserve in this impeccable 2021-built home in Tatum, TX.
